{
  "texts": [
    "However, certain manners can in turn control the type, quality and structure of the responses.",
    "The commands and strategies used to control the responses are then examples of so-called prompting.",
    "Prompting can be seen as a kind of programming language, but it is model-specific.",
    "For example, with the same natural language input, the output of a GPT-3 may be different from that of a GPT-4.",
    "Generally, new updates can completely change the way these models interact, which means that a new grammar or language must be learned for each model."
  ]
}